OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a bright day with
OL,6,Fsunny spells and occasional showers.
OL,7,FThe showers most frequent in the west,
OL,8,Fwintry on hills. Best of the sunshine
OL,9,Fthrough Angus and Fife. Chilly
OL,10,Fwesterly winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FMost of the showers dying out
OL,13,Fthis evening with clear skies for a
OL,14,Ftime. Thickening cloud and patchy
OL,15,Flight rain then pushing in from the
OL,16,Fwest later in the night.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
