OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FPatchy light rain at first
OL,6,Fthrough the Trossachs and west.
OL,7,FOtherwise, bright or sunny spells
OL,8,Fdeveloping and feeling quite warm in
OL,9,Fany sunshine. Winds light or moderate
OL,10,Ffrom the southwest.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FA dry
OL,13,Fand bright start on Wednesday, but
OL,14,Frain later. Mainly dry on Thursday and
OL,15,FFriday, best of the brightness on
OL,16,FThursday with the odd shower possible
OL,17,Fon Friday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
